{"word":"ἀκάθαρτος","slug":"ἀκάθαρτος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀκάθαρτος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:καθαίρω'><el>καθαίρω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>uncleansed, unclean, impure</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Adverb'>adv.</a>, <el>ἀκαθάρτως ἔχειν</el> <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>of things, <i>not purged away</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}